extendedInfo.description: Ants take over your home screen! Touch them and they die, bleeding in an exaggerated fashion.*Customizable sizes, colors, and speeds.*Realistic appearance and movement.*Choose your own background image.Email me for comments/issues/etc. I can not respond to comments that you post in the marketplace.Live wallpapers WILL consume your battery, especially ones as active as this. That is just what they do. It is not a reason to leave a negative comment or rating!From the developer of:"Ladybugs Alive! Wallpaper"and"Frogs Alive! Wallpaper" (Release delayed due to school)
